direction: right

ORCH: orchestrator { style.fill: "#ffffff"; style.stroke: "#333333" }
O: order { style.fill: "#ffffff"; style.stroke: "#333333" }
P: product { style.fill: "#ffffff"; style.stroke: "#333333" }
D: delivery { style.fill: "#ffffff"; style.stroke: "#333333" }

ORCH -> O: 주문 취소 { style.stroke: "#cc0000" }
ORCH -> P: 재고 복구 { style.stroke: "#cc0000" }
ORCH -> D: 배달 취소 { style.stroke: "#cc0000" }
